parameters.query:
WITH ParentChild as (
    SELECT Parent.AccountNumber parentAccountNumber, Parent.Id parentAccountId, Child.AccountNumber childAccountNumber,
       CASE WHEN Child.AccountNumber is null THEN (SELECT ParentId FROM Account WHERE AccountNumber = ParentChildMap.childCustomerReferenceNumber OR BPay__c = ParentChildMap.childCustomerReferenceNumber)
    ELSE null END AS realParentId
    FROM 
        (SELECT '{"data": {{ Data.parentChildMap | to_json }} }' Json) tmp1
         CROSS JOIN UNNEST (
            CAST(
                    JSON_EXTRACT(tmp1.Json, '$.data') as ARRAY(ROW(parentAccountNumber VARCHAR, childCustomerReferenceNumber VARCHAR))
                )
        ) as ParentChildMap (parentAccountNumber, childCustomerReferenceNumber)
    INNER JOIN Account Parent ON Parent.AccountNumber = ParentChildMap.parentAccountNumber
    LEFT JOIN Account Child ON (Child.AccountNumber = ParentChildMap.childCustomerReferenceNumber OR Child.BPay__c = ParentChildMap.childCustomerReferenceNumber) AND Parent.Id = Child.ParentId
    WHERE trim(Parent.Media_Agency__c) != ''
),
ParentInfo as (
    SELECT ParentChildValid.parentAccountId, Input.*
    FROM 
        (SELECT '{"data": {{Data.splitInfo | to_json }} }' Json) tmp2
         CROSS JOIN UNNEST (
            CAST(
                JSON_EXTRACT(tmp2.Json,'$.data')
                    as ARRAY(ROW(parentAccountNumber VARCHAR, parentPaymentNumber VARCHAR, splitTotal DECIMAL(10,2)))
            )
          ) as Input (parentAccountNumber, parentPaymentNumber, splitTotal)
        INNER JOIN
          (
              SELECT distinct parentAccountNumber, parentAccountId FROM ParentChild WHERE NOT EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM ParentChild ParentChild2 WHERE ParentChild2.realParentId = ParentChild.parentAccountId)
              EXCEPT
              SELECT distinct parentAccountNumber, parentAccountId FROM ParentChild WHERE childAccountNumber is null
          ) ParentChildValid
        ON ParentChildValid.parentAccountNumber = Input.parentAccountNumber
)
SELECT
  ParentInfo.parentAccountId AccountId, 
  ParentInfo.parentAccountNumber AccountNumber, 
  Payment.Id PaymentId,
  Payment.PaymentNumber PaymentNumber,
  ParentInfo.splitTotal SplitTotal
FROM ParentInfo
INNER JOIN Payment ON Payment.AccountId = ParentInfo.parentAccountId
WHERE Payment.PaymentNumber = ParentInfo.parentPaymentNumber
    AND Payment.Status = 'Processed' AND ParentInfo.splitTotal <= Payment.Amount - Payment.AppliedAmount
AND NOT EXISTS (
           SELECT Id from DebitMemo WHERE AccountId = ParentInfo.parentAccountId AND Comments = '{{Data.SFTPDownload.Downloaded[0].filename}}')

product.Business__c

WITH InputData as (SELECT * FROM (VALUES 
{%-for item in Data.Rebilling  -%}
    (
    CAST('{{ item.InvoiceNumber}}' as VARCHAR),
    CAST('{{ item.ActionToPerform}}' as VARCHAR),
    CAST('{{ item.SubscriptionRatePlanCharge}}' as VARCHAR),
    CAST('{{ item.Startdate}}' as VARCHAR),
    CAST('{{ item.RebillingCode}}' as VARCHAR),
    CAST('{{ item.ReasonCode}}' as VARCHAR),
    CAST('{{ item.Duration}}' as VARCHAR),
    CAST('{{ item.AdditionalComment}}' as VARCHAR),
    CAST('{{ item.SkipValidation}}' as VARCHAR)
    )

    {%-if forloop.last != true-%},{%-endif-%}
{%-endfor-%}
) 
AS t (InvoiceNumber,ActionToPerform,SubscriptionRatePlanCharge,Startdate,RebillingCode,ReasonCode,Duration,AdditionalComment,SkipValidation))


Select InD.*,
        max(CASE
        WHEN i.id is null  then 'The invoice does not exist'
        WHEN i.status IN('Canceled','CancelInProgress') then 'Canceled'
        WHEN i.status !='Posted' then 'Wrong Status'
        END) AS Status,
        max(a.IsCommodityCustomer__c) Commodity,
        max(i.code__c )InvoiceCode,
        max(i.TargetDate) as TargetDate,
            MIN(ii.ServiceStartDate) AS SubStartDate,
        array_agg(CAST(ROW(II.ServiceStartDate, suba.name,ii.discountamount) AS ROW("ServiceStartDate" VARCHAR, "subname" VARCHAR, "DiscountAmount" DECIMAL))) AS AggregateSubStartDate,
     array_agg(CAST(ROW(II.ServiceEndDate, suba.name,ii.discountamount) AS ROW("ServiceStartDate" VARCHAR, "subname" VARCHAR, "DiscountAmount" DECIMAL))) AS AggregateSubEndDate,
    MAX(ii.ServiceEndDate) as SubEndDate,
       		 max(CASE
        WHEN  coalesce(a.SequenceSetId,'') = '' THEN '8a28fd456b6e1f16016b71856a1275a9' 
        ELSE a.SequenceSetId
        END) AS OriginalSequenceSet,
          max(a.id) AccountId,
               max(
            CASE 
                WHEN InD.RebillingCode in ('R1','R4')AND a.EntityAccountNumber__c='ES5R' 
                THEN CASE
                    WHEN a.XC_Segment__c='B2C'   THEN 'RNORM'
                    WHEN a.XC_Segment__c='B2G'   THEN 'RNORMB2G'
                    WHEN a.XC_Segment__c='B2B'   THEN 'RNORMB2B'
                END
                WHEN (InD.RebillingCode ='R5' AND a.EntityAccountNumber__c='ES5R' ) THEN 'RSIMPL'
            END

        ) newSequenceSetID,
            array_distinct(array_agg(CAST(ROW(
    pp.paymentid,
    pp.amount
    
    ) 
    AS ROW(
    "PaymentId" VARCHAR,
    "Amount" DECIMAL(18,2)
    

    )))) 
    as AggregatePayment,
        array_distinct(array_agg(CAST(ROW(
    ii.chargename,
    suba.name,
    rp.name
    
    ) 
    AS ROW(
    "chargename" VARCHAR,
    "Subscription" VARCHAR,
    "item" VARCHAR

    )))) 
    as AggregateInvoice,
        max(i.id)InvoiceId,
      max(i.InvoiceDate) as InvoiceDate
from InputData InD 
LEFT JOIN invoice i  on i.invoiceNumber = InD.invoiceNumber 
 LEFT JOIN invoiceitem ii  on ii.invoiceid = i.id
  LEFT JOIN subscription suba on suba.id = ii.subscriptionid

left join RatePlan rp on ii.rateplanid = rp.id
LEFT JOIN subscription sub on sub.name = split(InD.SubscriptionRatePlanCharge,'|')[1]
LEFT JOIN Account a on a.id = i.AccountId
LEFT JOIN paymentpart pp on pp.InvoiceId= i.id
 WHERE II.PROCESSINGTYPE = '0'
group by  InD.InvoiceNumber,InD.ActionToPerform,InD.SubscriptionRatePlanCharge,InD.Startdate,InD.RebillingCode,InD.ReasonCode,InD.Duration,InD.AdditionalComment,InD.SkipValidation

Select    VAL__c Request,
				Description__c Reason
from default__listofvalues
where WorkflowInstanceName__c ='{{WorkflowInstance.name}}' and ActiveFlag__c=true

parameters.query:
WITH InputData as (SELECT * FROM (VALUES 
{%-for item in Data.Rebilling  -%}
    (
    CAST('{{ item.InvoiceNumber}}' as VARCHAR),
    CAST('{{ item.ActionToPerform}}' as VARCHAR),
    CAST('{{ item.SubscriptionRatePlanCharge}}' as VARCHAR),
    CAST('{{ item.Startdate}}' as VARCHAR),
    CAST('{{ item.RebillingCode}}' as VARCHAR),
    CAST('{{ item.ReasonCode}}' as VARCHAR),
    CAST('{{ item.Duration}}' as VARCHAR),
    CAST('{{ item.AdditionalComment}}' as VARCHAR),
    CAST('{{ item.SkipValidation}}' as VARCHAR)
    )

    {%-if forloop.last != true-%},{%-endif-%}
{%-endfor-%}
) 
AS t (InvoiceNumber,ActionToPerform,SubscriptionRatePlanCharge,Startdate,RebillingCode,ReasonCode,Duration,AdditionalComment,SkipValidation))


Select InD.*,
        max(CASE
        WHEN i.id is null  then 'The invoice does not exist'
        WHEN i.status IN('Canceled','CancelInProgress') then 'Canceled'
        WHEN i.status !='Posted' then 'Wrong Status'
        END) AS Status,
        max(a.IsCommodityCustomer__c) Commodity,
        max(i.code__c )InvoiceCode,
        max(i.TargetDate) as TargetDate,
            MIN(ii.ServiceStartDate) AS SubStartDate,
        array_agg(CAST(ROW(II.ServiceStartDate, suba.name,ii.discountamount) AS ROW("ServiceStartDate" VARCHAR, "subname" VARCHAR, "DiscountAmount" DECIMAL))) AS AggregateSubStartDate,
     array_agg(CAST(ROW(II.ServiceEndDate, suba.name,ii.discountamount) AS ROW("ServiceStartDate" VARCHAR, "subname" VARCHAR, "DiscountAmount" DECIMAL))) AS AggregateSubEndDate,
    MAX(ii.ServiceEndDate) as SubEndDate,
       		 max(CASE
        WHEN  coalesce(a.SequenceSetId,'') = '' THEN '8a28fd456b6e1f16016b71856a1275a9' 
        ELSE a.SequenceSetId
        END) AS OriginalSequenceSet,
          max(a.id) AccountId,
               max(
            CASE 
                WHEN InD.RebillingCode in ('R1','R4')AND a.EntityAccountNumber__c='ES5R' 
                THEN CASE
                    WHEN a.XC_Segment__c='B2C'   THEN 'RNORM'
                    WHEN a.XC_Segment__c='B2G'   THEN 'RNORMB2G'
                    WHEN a.XC_Segment__c='B2B'   THEN 'RNORMB2B'
                END
                WHEN (InD.RebillingCode ='R5' AND a.EntityAccountNumber__c='ES5R' ) THEN 'RSIMPL'
            END

        ) newSequenceSetID,
            array_distinct(array_agg(CAST(ROW(
    pp.paymentid,
    pp.amount
    
    ) 
    AS ROW(
    "PaymentId" VARCHAR,
    "Amount" DECIMAL(18,2)
    

    )))) 
    as AggregatePayment,
        array_distinct(array_agg(CAST(ROW(
    ii.chargename,
    suba.name,
    rp.name
    
    ) 
    AS ROW(
    "chargename" VARCHAR,
    "Subscription" VARCHAR,
    "item" VARCHAR

    )))) 
    as AggregateInvoice,
        max(i.id)InvoiceId,
      max(i.InvoiceDate) as InvoiceDate
from InputData InD 
LEFT JOIN invoice i  on i.invoiceNumber = InD.invoiceNumber 
 LEFT JOIN invoiceitem ii  on ii.invoiceid = i.id
  LEFT JOIN subscription suba on suba.id = ii.subscriptionid

left join RatePlan rp on ii.rateplanid = rp.id
LEFT JOIN subscription sub on sub.name = split(InD.SubscriptionRatePlanCharge,'|')[1]
LEFT JOIN Account a on a.id = i.AccountId
LEFT JOIN paymentpart pp on pp.InvoiceId= i.id
 WHERE II.PROCESSINGTYPE = '0'
group by  InD.InvoiceNumber,InD.ActionToPerform,InD.SubscriptionRatePlanCharge,InD.Startdate,InD.RebillingCode,InD.ReasonCode,InD.Duration,InD.AdditionalComment,InD.SkipValidation

Select    VAL__c Request,
				Description__c Reason
from default__listofvalues
where WorkflowInstanceName__c ='{{WorkflowInstance.name}}' and ActiveFlag__c=true

parameters.query:
SELECT RPC.ID AS "CHARGEID", RPC.NAME AS "CHARGENAME", RPC.CHARGENUMBER, S.NAME AS "SUBSCRIPTIONNAME", 
RP.ID AS RATEPLANID,RPCT.PRICE, RPCT.CURRENCY, RPC.EFFECTIVESTARTDATE, RPC.EFFECTIVEENDDATE, 
RPC.CHARGEDTHROUGHDATE, RPC.SPECIFICBILLINGPERIOD "BILLINGPERIODINMONTHS" , A.ACCOUNTNUMBER,
RPC.PRODUCTRATEPLANCHARGEID, PRPC.PRODUCTRATEPLANID, RP.NAME, RPC.LISTPRICEBASE,RPC.QUANTITY,
RPCT.PRICE,RPC.GROSSAMOUNT__C,RPC.REVENUELISTPRICE__C,RPC.DISCOUNTAMOUNT__C,RPC.SAC__C,
RPC.HSN__C,RPC.SFORDERTYPE__C,RPC.SFORDERLINE__C,RPC.SFQUOTELINETYPE__C,
RPC.DISCOUNTDECIMAL__C,RPC.SSPCUSTOMERTYPE__C,RPC.SSPSUBREGION__C,RPC.SSPPRODUCTGROUP__C,
RPC.SSPCOMBINEDCHANNEL__C,RPC.ASSOCIATEDQUOTELINENUMBER__C,
RPC.SFSUBSCRIPTIONLINEID__C,RPC.SALESORDERDATE__C, 
CASE WHEN RPC.SPLITAPPLICABLE__C =  '' THEN 'False' ELSE  RPC.SPLITAPPLICABLE__C END as SPLITAPPLICABLE__C , 
RP.NEWSKU__C,RP.OLDSKU__C,
RP.SKUDESCRIPTION__C,
S.SFORDERNUMBER__C,
S.ID AS "SUBSCRIPTIONID"
FROM RATEPLANCHARGE RPC
JOIN SUBSCRIPTION S ON RPC.SUBSCRIPTIONID = S.ID 
JOIN RATEPLANCHARGETIER RPCT ON RPCT.RATEPLANCHARGEID = RPC.ID
JOIN RATEPLAN RP ON RP.SUBSCRIPTIONID=S.ID
JOIN ACCOUNT A ON S.InvoiceOwnerId= A.ID
JOIN PRODUCTRATEPLANCHARGE PRPC ON PRPC.ID = RPC.PRODUCTRATEPLANCHARGEID
WHERE RPC.CHARGETYPE = 'Recurring'
AND RPC.EFFECTIVEENDDATE != RPC.CHARGEDTHROUGHDATE
AND S.STATUS= 'Active'
AND S.SubscriptionEndDate > date(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP AT TIME ZONE 'America/Los_Angeles')
AND RPC.SFORDERLINE__C IS NOT NULL
AND RPC.RevenueListPrice__c IS NOT NULL
AND S.TermChanged__c IS  NULL
ORDER BY RPC.EFFECTIVESTARTDATE DESC
Limit 10

workflow.description: This template shows how to use data source export and convert JSON payload to XML document. The workflow continues by taking the XML document and converting it to another XML document that could be consumed by state tax authority. One may need to update the XSLT transform to ensure the conversion from original XML document to new document is in format desired by state. Once final XML document is created, it could be sent to remote endpoints via FTP/SFTP.

  <xsl:output method="xml" indent="yes" version="1.0" />
  <xsl:template match="/Data">
    <xsl:element name="output">
      <xsl:element name="Account">
        <xsl:element name="Address1">
          <xsl:value-of select="BillToContact/Address1"/>
        </xsl:element>

      </xsl:element>
      <xsl:element name="Invoice">

          <xsl:value-of select="Invoice/Id"/>
        </xsl:element>

          <xsl:value-of select="Invoice/InvoiceNumber"/>
        </xsl:element>
        <xsl:element name="Balance">
